meanings: (사람을) meet, see; (처음으로) (formal) encounter; (우연히) come across, run[bump] into
작별 It was good to see you.
작별 It was nice to see you.

phrases.phrase: 당신을 만나게 될 줄 꿈에도 생각지 못했습니다.
meanings: 소개 I never dreamed I could meet you.

phrases.phrase: 이렇게 빨리 만나게 될 줄은 미처 생각 못했습니다.
meanings: 대화 시작 I didn't think I'd see you so soon.

phrases.phrase: 조바심 내지 말아요. 곧 누군가를 만나게 될 겁니다.
meanings: 이성교제 You just have to be patient. You'll meet someone soon.

meanings.meaning: Look (at) what the cat dragged[brought] in!
I'm glad I bumped into you.
